3302. 		/// - High 64 bits: <see cref="P:System.DateTimeOffset.Ticks" /> from the timestamp
3303. 		/// - Low 64 bits: A globally monotonically increasing counter
3304. 		/// </para>
3305. 		/// <para>
3306. 		/// The resulting string is strictly monotonically increasing when compared lexicographically,
3307. 		/// which is required for keyset pagination to work correctly. Unlike <c>Guid.CreateVersion7</c>,
3308. 		/// which uses random bits for intra-millisecond uniqueness, this implementation guarantees
3309. 		/// strict ordering for all identifiers regardless of when they were created.
3310. 		/// </para>
